column16: Alexei Ramirez flies out to left fielder David Murphy.
A.  J.   Pierzynski hits a grand slam (3) to right center field.   Jim Thome scores.    Brent Lillibridge scores.    Paul Konerko scores.
Paul Konerko walks.    Jim Thome to 3rd.    Brent Lillibridge to 2nd.
Jermaine Dye hit by pitch.    Jim Thome to 2nd.
Jim Thome singles on a line drive to right fielder Nelson Cruz.
Carlos Quentin lines out sharply to left fielder David Murphy.
Josh Fields flies out to center fielder Marlon Byrd.
